    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three primary QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percentage difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted based on the standard regulatory standing of ASTM F1717 and corroborating literature. The inherent variability in the force-at-40mm QoI was reviewed qualitatively and judged low-risk given the narrow experimental coefficient of variation (2.9%). Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence COU.",
